                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                    h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 매크로 실행
                                    p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{macroCountSummary()}}
                                div(class="space-y-4 px-4 py-4")
                                    label(class="block")
                                        span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행할 매크로
                                        wiz-component-search-select([items]="macroSelectorItems()", [value]="selectedMacroId()", (valueChange)="selectMacro($event)", [placeholder]="'실행할 매크로를 선택하세요'", [searchPlaceholder]="'이름 또는 설명으로 검색'", [emptyText]="'실행할 수 있는 매크로가 없습니다.'", [disabled]="macroLoading()")
                                    div(*ngIf="macroError()", class="rounded-md border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-amber-700 dark:border-amber-900/70 dark:bg-amber-950/40 dark:text-amber-300") {{macroError()}}
                                    div(*ngIf="!selectedMacro() && !macroLoading()", class="rounded-md border border-dashed border-zinc-300 px-4 py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행할 매크로를 선택하세요.
                                    div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto]")
                                        div(class="space-y-3")
                                            label(class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200")
                                                input(type="checkbox", [ngModel]="macroArgsEnabled()", (ngModelChange)="macroArgsEnabled.set($event)", class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-zinc-300 text-zinc-950 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700")
                                                span 실행 인자 사용
                                            label(*ngIf="macroArgsEnabled()", class="block")
                                                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 실행 인자
                                                input(type="text", [ngModel]="macroArgsInput()", (ngModelChange)="macroArgsInput.set($event)", placeholder="예: --force prod", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                                        button(type="button", (click)="runSelectedMacro()", [disabled]="busy() || !selectedMacro() || selectedMacro()?.enabled === false", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200 lg:self-end")
                                            i(class="fa-solid fa-play")
                                            span 실행
                                    div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                        div(class="border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                            h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 실행 결과
                                        div(*ngIf="!macroRunResult()", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 아직 실행 결과가 없습니다.
                                        div(*ngIf="macroRunResult()", class="space-y-3 px-4 py-4")
                                            div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                                p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{macroRunResult()?.macro?.name}}
                                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(macroRunStatus())") {{statusLabel(macroRunStatus())}}
                                            p(class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{formatDate(macroRunResult()?.operation?.updated_at || macroRunResult()?.operation?.created_at)}}
                                            pre(*ngIf="macroRunLogText()", class="max-h-[420px] overflow-auto rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-100") {{macroRunLogText()}}
                            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
                                div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                    div
                                        h2(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 이 서버 전용 매크로
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{nodeMacros().length}}개
                                    button(type="button", (click)="openAddMacro()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                                        span 추가
                                div(*ngIf="nodeMacros().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이 서버에만 보이는 매크로가 없습니다.
                                div(*ngFor="let macro of nodeMacros()", class="border-t border-zinc-100 px-4 py-4 first:border-t-0 dark:border-zinc-800")
                                    div(class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3")
                                        div(class="min-w-0")
                                            div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                                p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{macro.name}}
                                                span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-0.5 text-[11px] font-semibold", [ngClass]="macro.enabled ? statusClass('ok') : statusClass('warning')") {{macro.enabled ? '사용 가능' : '비활성화'}}
                                            p(*ngIf="macro.description", class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{macro.description}}
                                        div(class="flex items-center gap-2")
                                            button(type="button", (click)="openEditMacro(macro)", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                                i(class="fa-solid fa-pen")
                                            button(type="button", (click)="deleteMacro(macro)", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md border border-rose-300 text-rose-700 hover:bg-rose-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-rose-900/70 dark:text-rose-300 dark:hover:bg-rose-950/30")
                                                i(class="fa-solid fa-trash")

                    section(*ngIf="isDetailTab('terminal')", class="p-4", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'min-h-[calc(100vh-180px)]' : 'space-y-4'")
                        div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'flex min-h-[calc(100vh-210px)] flex-col' : ''")
                            div(class="flex flex-col gap-3 border-b border-zinc-200 px-4 py-3 dark:border-zinc-800 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    span(class="inline-flex rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="terminalConnected() ? statusClass('ok') : (terminalConnecting() ? statusClass('pending') : statusClass('unknown'))") {{terminalStatus()}}
                                div(class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                                    button(type="button", data-testid="servers-terminal-expand-toggle", (click)="toggleTerminalExpanded()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'fa-compress' : 'fa-expand'")
                                        span {{terminalExpandLabel()}}
                                    button(type="button", (click)="disconnectTerminal()", [disabled]="!terminalConnected() && !terminalConnecting()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plug-circle-xmark")
                                        span 연결 종료
                                    button(type="button", (click)="clearTerminal()", [disabled]="!terminalConnected()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-eraser")
                                        span 화면 지우기
                            div(class="p-4", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'flex flex-1 flex-col' : ''")
                                div(class="mb-4 flex flex-col gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-4 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between")
                                    div
                                        p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 웹 터미널
                                        p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{terminalDescription()}}
                                        p(*ngIf="terminalError()", class="mt-2 text-xs text-rose-600 dark:text-rose-300") {{terminalError()}}
                                    button(type="button", (click)="connectTerminal()", [disabled]="busy() || terminalConnecting()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-50 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                                        i(class="fa-solid fa-plug")
                                        span {{terminalConnected() ? '다시 연결' : '터미널 연결'}}
                                div(data-testid="servers-terminal-host", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-800 bg-black", [ngClass]="terminalExpandedView() ? 'min-h-[calc(100vh-340px)] flex-1' : 'min-h-[460px]'")

div(*ngIf="serverModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeServerModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-lg rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{serverModalTitle()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeServerModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 px-5 py-4")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서버 IP 또는 host
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.host", placeholder="192.168.0.15", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_120px]")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 계정
                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.username", placeholder="root", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 포트
                    input(type="number", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.ssh_port", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") SSH 비밀번호 {{isEditing() ? '(선택)' : ''}}
                input(type="password", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.password", autocomplete="new-password", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(*ngIf="isEditing()", class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 비워두면 저장된 SSH key로 다시 연결 확인한 뒤 저장합니다.
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시 이름
                input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="serverForm.name", placeholder="비워두면 host를 사용합니다", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeServerModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveServer()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-key")
                span {{serverSubmitLabel()}}

div(*ngIf="fileBrowserOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeFileBrowser()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-3xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900", data-testid="servers-compose-browser")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") Compose 파일 선택
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{importCandidate()?.name || importCandidate()?.id || '선택한 서버'}}의 docker-compose.yaml 또는 docker-compose.yml 파일을 서비스 생성 화면으로 가져옵니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeFileBrowser()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-4 px-5 py-4")
            label(class="block")
                span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 이름
                input(data-testid="servers-compose-service-name", type="text", [ngModel]="composeImportName()", (ngModelChange)="composeImportName.set($event)", placeholder="예: 사내 게시판", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 서비스 생성 화면에서 이름, 도메인, 배포 전 점검을 이어서 확인합니다.
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-2 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_auto_auto_auto]")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 경로
                    input(data-testid="servers-compose-path", type="text", [ngModel]="fileBrowserInput()", (ngModelChange)="fileBrowserInput.set($event)", (keydown.enter)="jumpToBrowsePath()", placeholder="예: /home/admin 또는 ~/stack", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                button(type="button", (click)="jumpToBrowsePath()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right")
                    span 이동
                button(type="button", (click)="browseFiles('')", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-house")
                    span 홈
                button(type="button", (click)="toggleHiddenFiles()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800 lg:self-end")
                    i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="fileBrowserShowHidden() ? 'fa-eye-slash' : 'fa-eye'")
                    span {{fileBrowserShowHidden() ? '숨김 감추기' : '숨김 보기'}}
            div(*ngIf="!fileBrowserPath() && fileBrowserBusy()", class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-2 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-400")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-spinner fa-spin")
                span 등록된 사용자 홈 디렉토리를 확인하는 중입니다.
            div(*ngIf="fileBrowserPath()", class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2")
                button(*ngFor="let crumb of fileBrowserCrumbs()", type="button", (click)="browseFiles(crumb.path)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") {{crumb.label}}
                button(*ngIf="fileBrowserPath() !== '/'", type="button", (click)="browseParent()", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                    i(class="fa-solid fa-arrow-up")
                    span 상위 폴더
            div(class="max-h-[420px] overflow-auto rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                div(*ngIf="fileBrowserBusy() && fileBrowserItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 파일 목록을 불러오는 중입니다.
                div(*ngIf="!fileBrowserBusy() && fileBrowserItems().length === 0", class="px-4 py-10 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 파일이 없습니다.
                div(*ngFor="let item of fileBrowserItems()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 border-b border-zinc-100 px-4 py-3 last:border-b-0 dark:border-zinc-800")
                    div(class="min-w-0")
                        button(*ngIf="item.type === 'folder'", type="button", (click)="browseFiles(item.path)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy()", class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-left text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 hover:text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-50 dark:hover:text-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-folder text-amber-500")
                            span(class="truncate") {{item.name}}
                        div(*ngIf="item.type !== 'folder'", class="flex items-center gap-2")
                            i(class="fa-solid", [ngClass]="canImportFile(item) ? 'fa-file-code text-sky-500' : 'fa-file text-zinc-400'")
                            p(class="truncate text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{item.name}}
                        p(class="mt-1 truncate text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{item.path}}
                    div(class="flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2")
                        span(*ngIf="item.type === 'folder'", class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 폴더
                        span(*ngIf="item.type === 'file' && !canImportFile(item)", class="text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 등록 불가
                        button(*ngIf="canImportFile(item)", type="button", (click)="importComposeFile(item)", [disabled]="fileBrowserBusy() || !composeImportNameValue()", class="inline-flex h-8 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-2.5 text-xs font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                            i(class="fa-solid fa-plus")
                            span 생성 화면으로 이동

div(*ngIf="macroModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeMacroModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-5xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            div
                h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{macroModalTitle()}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") Bash 스크립트를 저장해두고 선택한 서버에서 반복 실행할 수 있습니다.
            button(type="button", (click)="closeMacroModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 disabled:opacity-50 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 px-5 py-4 lg:grid-cols-[320px_1fr]")
            div(class="space-y-4")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 이름
                    input(type="text", [(ngModel)]="macroForm.name", placeholder="예: 서비스 점검", class="h-10 w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                label(class="block")
                    span(class="mb-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 설명
                    textarea([(ngModel)]="macroForm.description", rows="4", placeholder="이 매크로가 어떤 작업을 하는지 간단히 적어주세요.", class="w-full rounded-md border border-zinc-300 bg-white px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-900 placeholder:text-zinc-400 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-100")
                label(class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm text-zinc-700 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200")
                    input(type="checkbox", [(ngModel)]="macroForm.enabled", class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-zinc-300 text-zinc-950 focus:ring-zinc-500 dark:border-zinc-700")
                    span 저장 후 바로 실행할 수 있도록 사용 상태로 둡니다.
                div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 px-3 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-600 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-400")
                    p 인자는 실행 시마다 따로 입력합니다.
                    p(class="mt-1") 스크립트 안에서는 `$1`, `$2`, `$@` 형태로 받을 수 있습니다.
            div(class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800")
                nu-monaco-editor([(ngModel)]="macroForm.script", [options]="macroEditorOptions", height="420px")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-end gap-2 border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeMacroModal()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md border border-zinc-300 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-700 hover:bg-zinc-50 disabled:opacity-50 dark:border-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-200 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800") 취소
            button(type="button", (click)="saveMacro()", [disabled]="busy()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-2 rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 disabled:opacity-60 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-floppy-disk")
                span {{macroSubmitLabel()}}

div(*ngIf="actionModalOpen()", class="fixed inset-0 z-40 flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-6")
    div(class="absolute inset-0 bg-zinc-950/50", (click)="closeActionModal()")
    section(class="relative w-full max-w-xl rounded-md border border-zinc-200 bg-white shadow-xl dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900")
        div(class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            h2(class="text-base font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{actionTitle()}}
            button(type="button", (click)="closeActionModal()", class="inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-md text-zinc-500 hover:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-400 dark:hover:bg-zinc-800")
                i(class="fa-solid fa-xmark")
        div(class="space-y-3 px-5 py-4")
            div(*ngFor="let row of actionRows()", class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3 rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-2 dark:border-zinc-800")
                div(class="min-w-0")
                    p(class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{row.name}}
                    p(*ngIf="row.value", class="mt-0.5 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{row.value}}
                span(class="inline-flex shrink-0 rounded-md border px-2 py-1 text-xs font-semibold", [ngClass]="statusClass(row.status)") {{statusLabel(row.status)}}
            div(*ngIf="actionResult()?.service", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 text-sm dark:border-zinc-800")
                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") {{actionResult()?.service?.name || actionResult()?.service?.namespace}}
                p(class="mt-1 break-all text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{actionResult()?.compose_path || '-'}}
            div(*ngIf="actionResult()?.operation", class="rounded-md border border-zinc-200 px-3 py-3 text-sm dark:border-zinc-800")
                p(class="font-semibold text-zinc-950 dark:text-zinc-50") 작업 {{actionResult()?.operation?.status || '-'}}
                p(class="mt-1 text-xs text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") {{actionResult()?.operation?.type || 'operation'}} · {{actionResult()?.macro?.name || '-'}}
                pre(*ngIf="actionOperationLogText()", class="mt-3 max-h-72 overflow-auto rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 py-3 text-xs text-zinc-100") {{actionOperationLogText()}}
            div(*ngIf="actionRows().length === 0 && !actionResult()?.service", class="py-8 text-center text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400") 표시할 결과가 없습니다.
        div(class="flex justify-end border-t border-zinc-200 px-5 py-4 dark:border-zinc-800")
            button(type="button", (click)="closeActionModal()", class="inline-flex h-9 items-center rounded-md bg-zinc-950 px-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-100 dark:text-zinc-950 dark:hover:bg-zinc-200") 확인
